race.comment: DEAR CARLA LOU (4) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 21.67 beating HARA HACHI BU. Winner at her latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Can measure up again. CROYDON (2) could not have been more impressive last start in his scintillating 21.69 win at this track over 390m. Top win latest and rates a key player again. HARA HACHI BU (1) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish 2.25 lengths back in second (21.81) at this track in a Grade 5 H over 390m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Will give a great sight again. PAW MANTRA (3) comes off a big run when finishing second in a blistering 21.95 last time. Has claims on that run.
